<html>
	<head>
		<title>로그인</title>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/milligram/1.4.1/milligram.min.css">
		<style>
			.register-button {
				background-color: #ffffff; /* 배경색을 하얀색으로 설정 */
				border: 1px solid #a347cb; /* 테두리 추가 */
				color: #333; /* 텍스트 색상 */
			}
			.button {
				margin: 15px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<h1>로그인</h1>
			<form method="post" action="/login" class="signup-form">
				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="email">이메일주소</label>
					<input type="text" name="email" required />
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="password">비밀번호</label>
					<input type="password" id="password" name="password" required />
				</div>
				<button type="submit" class="button centered-text">로그인</button>
			</form>
			<div>
				<p>
					아직 회원이 아니신가요? 회원가입 하러 가기:
					<a href="/register" class="button register-button">회원가입</a>
				</p>
				
			</div>
			
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
